{"tid":972274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"寫真賣20萬本破紀錄 生田繪梨花乳戰白石麻衣","createTime":"2019-01-07T09:28:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T16:38:22.000Z","uid":147522,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"25ee58c8febaa0ffa487afa789e97186a0be5eb3","tid":972274,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kuQBpxi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkuQBpxi.png&h=17712e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本夯團「乃木坂46」21歲人氣成員生田繪梨花從鄰家女孩搖身一變成為性感女神，她在22日推出的最新寫真集《Intermission》中，以性感蕾絲內衣入鏡，凹凸有致的魔鬼好身材一覽無遺。目前寫真集首批出貨量已高達20萬本，創下出版的「講談社」創業110年來的寫真集最高出貨量紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n「乃木坂46」近來人氣居高不下，已明顯超越對手女團「AKB48」，去年底還連霸「日本唱片大賞」，就連成員推出寫真集也成為銷售保證。<br />\n<br />\n生田繪梨花去年9月前往紐約的知名景點為寫真集取景，難得解禁性感，十分吸睛。 <br />\n同團隊友白石麻衣之前熱賣的寫真集《Passport》首批出貨只有10萬本，生田卻以2倍出貨量起跳，也被看好有望刷新《Passport》熱賣34萬本的紀錄。"},{"pid":"19910a72b73053ab2694d973d72e5a1aed38ad58","tid":972274,"uid":45213,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T10:12:33.000Z","msg":"乃木坂班女真心屈機"},{"pid":"a948c1d80ae68059a98774b65ea2c4a0b42d21d5","tid":972274,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T10:22:59.000Z","msg":"揸一下幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495ae6c70f4136f677efdb8a901bfae95a6b48dc","tid":972274,"uid":6879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T12:00:43.000Z","msg":"いくちゃん<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd78a5baf1d60a03a2d6603dcda3b5db07152470","tid":972274,"uid":22365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T12:31:05.000Z","msg":"fifty~~one 渣"},{"pid":"a469f1b35cfc9609bdab6b4d83a017b7f61124d9","tid":972274,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T12:33:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3eb18bbe1228e60532bb73c2453467c2c84207d2","tid":972274,"uid":69115,"like":0,"dislike":0